{"_id":"0vGrY6ABxgwVVs60","name":"Red Sign of Shddle M'ell","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"1 round","cost":{"mp":"3","san":"1d8","pow":"","hp":null,"other":"1 hit point per round"},"description":{"value":"<p>An awful spell that causes one or several victims to die horribly. The caster inscribes in the air the dreaded sign of Shudde M&rsquo;ell, while speaking words of power. When formed correctly, a dull red symbol glows in the air as the caster&rsquo;s finger describes it. The sign&rsquo;s malevolent effects manifest the round after its creation. Once formed, the sign must be maintained by concentration and the expenditure of 3 more magic points each additional round.</p>\n<p>All those within 10 yards of the sign lose [[/roll 1D3]] hit points per round as their bodies quake and spasm, and their internal organs and blood vessels convulse. Those further than 10 yards but nearer than 30 yards lose 1 hit point each round. Those further than 30 yards take no damage. It is possible to escape the sign&rsquo;s effect by crawling behind a stout wall or other opaque barrier. The caster must stand next to the sign and concentrate. The caster loses 1 hit point each round because of their proximity to the sign.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> <span class=\"fontstyle3\">The Red Sign, The Mark of Fiery Pain <br style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\" /><br /></p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":1500001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/deathzone.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"1ElW7qSP2Wm6hfmo","name":"Dominate","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"Instantaneous","cost":{"mp":"1","san":"1","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>Bends the will of the target to that of the caster. For the spell to take effect the caster must succeed in an opposed POW roll with the target. If successful, the target obeys the commands of the caster without exception until the next combat round concludes.</p>\n<p>The spell can affect only one individual at a time and has a maximum range of 10 yards. Obviously the command or commands must be intelligible to the target and the spell may be broken if a command contradicts the target&rsquo;s basic nature (such as instructing a human to fly). Dominate can be cast and recast as many times as the caster finds possible, allowing a target to be controlled without interruption for several minutes. Each cast of the spell has the same costs and limits. Recasting is instantaneous.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names</strong>: Command of the Wizard, The Chant of Possession, Baleful Influence.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":400001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/dominate.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"1sfJTP6a32Ht5jkG","name":"Song of Hastur","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"3 rounds before taking effect","cost":{"mp":"1D4 (per round)","san":"1D4 (per round)","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>A hideous wailing ululation by the caster causes the skin and flesh of the chosen victim to bubble and fester into pestilent blobs.</p>\n<p>The target must be visible to the caster. Though everyone can hear the song, the spell affects only the person chosen as target. This spell will not work except at night and only if the star Aldebaran is visible. A roll equal to or under the caster&rsquo;s POW must be made to sing the correct alien melody.</p>\n<p>Successfully cast, the spell causes the target [[/roll 1D6]] hit points damage per round the spell is active. After every two rounds, scarring reduces the victim&rsquo;s APP by [[/roll 3D10]]. After every four rounds, internal ruptures lower the victim&rsquo;s CON by [[/roll 3D10]]. When the victim&rsquo;s CON reaches 0 or death occurs from hit point loss, the body swells up and bursts with a sickening&mdash;pop!&mdash;as steamy gore spills onto the floor.</p>\n<p>The song can be used defensively, to guard against another caster of this spell. Successful opposing castings neutralize each other.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> The King&rsquo;s Cry, Music of the Court in Yellow, Bring Forth the Festering Boil of Great Agony and Torment</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":1700001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/song.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"4PCvPLuUpwItOkow","name":"Dread Curse of Azathoth","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"1 round","cost":{"mp":"4","san":"1d6","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>The sorcerer draws upon the energies of the Outer God to directly drain POW from a victim. By repeating the secret name of Azathoth, one can generate respect and fear in any being conversant with the Mythos, for to know the name implies that one knows the secret Last Syllable. Said alone, the Last Syllable may be directed against a foe. For the spell to take effect the caster must succeed in an opposed POW roll with the target. If the caster is successful, the target loses ][[/roll 3D6]] POW.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names</strong>: Utterance of the Last Syllable, Ye Doleful Leeching, By the True Name Thy Power is Sapped.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":500001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/curse.png","effects":[]}
{"name":"Breath of the Deep","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"1 round","cost":{"mp":"8","san":"1d6","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>The target&rsquo;s lungs fill with seawater, potentially causing an<br />unpleasant death by drowning.</p>\n<p>The caster must be able to see the target. After mentally intoning the spell for a round, for the spell to take effect the caster must win an opposed POW roll with the target. If the caster wins the target begins to drown&mdash;the target falls to the floor, choking on seawater and taking [[/roll 1d8]]&nbsp;damage each round. The target should make an Extreme CON roll (equal to or below one-fifth CON) after taking damage each round; if the roll is successful the water has been expelled and the effects of the spell cease. &nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> Currency of the Blue Sea, The Sailor&rsquo;s Curse, Kiss of Brine</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":100001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/drown.png","effects":[],"_id":"5AY99nwtPfxSIZVk"}
{"_id":"LID6FqJCm3OdHJ52","name":"Shriveling","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"Instantaneous","cost":{"mp":"variable magic points","san":"variable sanity points","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>A powerful offensive spell causing physical injury to a target. The caster invests as many magic points as desired and that number halved in Sanity points. For the spell to take effect the caster must succeed in an opposed POW roll with the target. If successful, the target is subjected to a sudden and terrifying blast of energy, causing flesh to blacken and wither. The target loses 1 hit point per magic point invested in the spell.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> <span class=\"fontstyle3\">Shriving, The Withering Blast of<br />Death, The Black Words <br style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\" /><br /></p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":1600001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/wound.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"NSXo9aZzV1MNLEod","name":"Fist of Yog-Sothoth","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"Instantaneous","cost":{"mp":"variable magic points","san":"1D6","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>The caster causes a massive, invisible force to hit a single target. The caster must be able to see the target.</p>\n<p>Each magic point invested in the spell yields [[/roll 2D10]] STR of force. For every 30 feet of distance that the caster stands from the target (after the first thirty feet), the caster must spend an additional magic point.</p>\n<p>When the target is struck (if a living thing), an opposed roll must be made using the spell&rsquo;s STR versus the target&rsquo;s CON. If successful, the target is knocked unconscious. Whether or not the target is left unconscious, the target is always pushed away from the caster for a distance in feet equal to the STR of the blow minus the target&rsquo;s SIZ.</p>\n<p>The spell can be used against the STR of inanimate objects such as doors or walls. Results may be obvious, but sometimes Keepers will have to determine these cases.</p>\n<p>For example: The caster spends 5 magic points to hit an investigator 50 feet away. 1 magic point is spent on the range. The other 4 generate a STR of [[/roll 8D10]] that are rolled for a result of 57. The investigator fails a Hard CON roll (since the spells STR is over 50) and so they are knocked unconscious. The investigator has a SIZ of 45 and is bowled back 12 feet by the impact.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> Channel the Strength of the Opener of the Way, Smite Down Thine Enemy, The Hideous Blast of the Foul One</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":false,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":800001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/fist.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"Z3OSQ6DTQl2EysCq","name":"Mental Suggestion","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"3 rounds","cost":{"mp":"variable magic points","san":"variable sanity points","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>The caster can command any being with human blood in its veins. A single target, who is visible to the unaided eye of the sorcerer, is affected. The victim carries out all that is commanded by the caster, even to self-destruction. The spell also works against Lengites, deep one hybrids, ghoul changelings, Little People, serpent folk and deep ones who have interbred with humans, but doesn&rsquo;t work on nonhuman entities such as shantaks or dimensional shamblers.</p>\n<p>The caster intones the spell and relates the suggestion to the target. For the spell to take effect the caster must succeed in an opposed POW roll with the target. Extreme suggestions involving death or great harm require a second opposed POW roll just before the suggestion is implemented.</p>\n<p>The cost for the spell varies with the suggestion. For ordinary unthreatening suggestions (drop your sword, hand over your money and leave, etc.), the cost is 5 magic points and [[/roll 1D3]] Sanity points. Riskier suggestions, but not ones antithetical to the target (go to Dunwich, set fire to a building, etc.), cost 10 magic points and [[/roll 2D3]] Sanity points. Dangerous or suicidal suggestions (kill a companion, kidnap the President, etc.) cost 15 magic points and [[/roll 3D3]] Sanity points.</p>\n<p>If used on an investigator the effects lasts for 1 round for each point of INT the caster possesses.If the INT of the investigator is higher than that of the caster, the caster must win another POW roll every 10 rounds. When the caster fails the spell is broken.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> Domination of the Will, Master and Servant, Bend Quarry to Thy Power, Mesmerise, Bend Will, Shake Resolve, Govern Mind, Implant Suggestion</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":false},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":1300001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/conman.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"ZsXSrw6l3v5gsi0v","name":"Enthrall Victim","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"1 round","cost":{"mp":"2","san":"1D6","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>The caster must be able to speak calmly with the target before the spell can take effect. After a round or so of talking, an opposed POW roll must be made between the caster and target on [[/roll 1D100]]. If overcome, the victim stands struck, numb and dumb, until relieved from the trance by physical assault or some similarly shocking event. If the caster fails to overcome the target, he or she may try the spell the following round.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> Strike Dumb, The Silver Beguiling Tongue.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":700001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/enthrall.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"b5hS5eE1j81G4TTC","name":"Melt Flesh (dead flesh)","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"5 rounds","cost":{"mp":"1 (per 15 SIZ of flesh)","san":"1D4","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>This devilish spell heats flesh (dead or living) to its melting point in one round. If used on animate flesh, the cost is substantially higher to the caster in magic points. The victim&rsquo;s flesh is melted causing horrific disfigurement ([[/roll 1D4]] damage per 15 SIZ points affected). In certain cases, such as where the face is targeted, the victim may become blind or lose the ability to hear, and possibly suffocate unless air vents can be quickly created. Seeing human flesh melt off human bones costs 1/[[/roll 1D6]] Sanity points.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong>&nbsp;Rite of the Dissolution, Liquefy Skin.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":1100001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/melt.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"bApMAB4sdKQeUxuu","name":"Dust of Suleiman","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"1 round to apply 1 dose","cost":{"mp":"10 (per 3 dose)","san":"","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>Creates a grey-green powder that harms unnatural beings from other planes of existence. The powder requires the dust from an Egyptian mummy at least 2,000 years old; each such mummy suffices for three doses of the magic dust. The ingredients also include frankincense, sulfur, and saltpeter. An incantation must be said over the dust while it is being sprinkled.</p>\n<p>Sprinkled over a being not of this Earth, the entity loses [[/roll 1D20]] hit points per dose. It takes one round to apply a dose. The powder works only on extraterrestrial and other planar beings, thus the powder would harm a dimensional shambler, Yog-Sothoth or a mi-go, but is useless against a shoggoth or a deep one.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> The Egyptian Powder, Protection of the Dead.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":600001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/powder.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"dwvM3ALAdQyHpzsL","name":"Melt Flesh (living flesh)","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"5 rounds","cost":{"mp":"5 (per 15 SIZ of flesh)","san":"1D6","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>This devilish spell heats flesh (dead or living) to its melting point in one round. If used on animate flesh, the cost is substantially higher to the caster in magic points. The victim&rsquo;s flesh is melted causing horrific disfigurement ([[/roll 1D4]] damage per 15 SIZ points affected). In certain cases, such as where the face is targeted, the victim may become blind or lose the ability to hear, and possibly suffocate unless air vents can be quickly created. Seeing human flesh melt off human bones costs 1/[[/roll 1D6]] Sanity points.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> Rite of the Dissolution, Liquefy Skin.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":1200001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/melt.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"f5P5jXGRPldeDfaE","name":"Wrack","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"1 round","cost":{"mp":"3","san":"1","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>This spell will temporarily incapacitate a single target who is within 10 yards of the caster. For the spell to take effect the caster must succeed in an opposed POW roll with the target. Intense, wracking pains seize the target, the face and hands blister and drip fluid, and the eyes cloud with blood and become temporarily sightless. The target is rendered completely helpless during the period of the spell&rsquo;s effect.</p>\n<p>The effect lasts [[/roll 1D6]] rounds, after which sight returns. In [[/roll 3D10]] minutes, the target fully recovers and can resume normal activity. Traces of physical corruption fade quickly and in 24 hours only faint blemishes can be seen on the skin. Each such experience costs the target 1/[[/roll 1D6+1]] Sanity points.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> Woeful Agony of the Wretched, The Festering Blindness of the Seven Hells, Rend Enemy</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":1900001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/pain.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"ftCzFiyjbbIqqIE8","name":"Implant Fear","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"Instantaneous","cost":{"mp":"12","san":"1D6","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>This spell causes soul-chilling dread, breaking the target&rsquo;s concentration and disrupting his or her actions. The caster must be able to see and point a finger at the target while invoking a curse.</p>\n<p>The sudden unnerving costs the target 0/[[/roll 1D6]] Sanity points and they feel compelled to retreat to a safe place&mdash; anywhere the person would normally feel safe and secure.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> <span class=\"fontstyle3\">Finger of Doom, Eibon&rsquo;s Jinx, The Evil Eye. <br style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\" /><br /></p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":false},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":1000001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/fear.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"kiw8mk1IvlTIm8Jd","name":"Wither Limb","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"Instantaneous","cost":{"mp":"8","san":"1D6","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>A terrifying spell designed to torment and cause permanent damage to a target. The caster must be within 10 yards of the target. For the spell to take effect the caster must succeed in an opposed POW roll with the target. If successful, the caster nominates an arm or leg. The said appendage rapidly and painfully withers and shrivels, causing [[/roll 1D8]] hit points of damage and a permanent loss of [[/roll 2D10]] CON. The victim loses [[/roll 1D4]]/[[/roll 1D8]] Sanity points. Alternative names: The Song of Pain, Shrivel Thy Enemy, The Wasting Burn.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":false,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":1800001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/limb.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"kqxf90U4Ni7b1b6W","name":"Death Spell","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"1d3","cost":{"mp":"24","san":"3d10","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>Reserved for only the most foul of sorcerers, this spell causes the bewildered victim to burst into flame. The target must be within ten yards of the caster. For the spell to take effect the caster must succeed in an opposed POW roll with the target during each round of concentration.</p>\n<p>After [[/roll 1D3]] rounds of concentration, the victim&rsquo;s skin forms large blisters and he or she loses [[/roll 1D3]] hit points. In the next round, the victim loses an additional [[/roll 1D6]] hit points.</p>\n<p>On the third round, the victim bursts into flames, losing [[/roll 1D10]] hit points then and each round thereafter. The stench of burning hair and flesh is overwhelming (all witnesses should make SAN rolls or lose 1/[[/roll 1D6]] SAN). It is impossible to render aid, since the horrified victim burns from the inside out.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> <span class=\"fontstyle3\">Ye Dreadful Pricking, The Curse of<br />Fiery Doom, Cthugha&rsquo;s Embrace.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":300001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/death.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"oeeN8lfOUzV6M2Cc","name":"Mindblast","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"Instantaneous","cost":{"mp":"10","san":"1D3","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>The victim of this spell suffers a terrible mental assault, causing the loss of 5 Sanity points and inducing temporary insanity. For the spell to take effect the caster must succeed in an opposed POW roll with the target.</p>\n<p>The target is affected as per the rules for temporary insanity, beginning with a bout of madness, and may continue to suffer from flashbacks and/or nightmares for days following.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> Curse of Enfeeblement, Wave of Doom, Abyss of the Mind&rsquo;s Eye</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":1400001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/mindblast.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"pCMxsnjut1AhIqWH","name":"Flesh Ward","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"5 rounds","cost":{"mp":"variable","san":"1D4","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>Grants protection against physical attack. Each magic point spent gives the caster (or the chosen target) [[/roll 1D6]] points of armor against non-magical attacks. This protection wears off as it blocks damage. For example, if a character had 12 points of Flesh Ward as armor and was hit for 8 points of damage, the Flesh Ward would be reduced to 4 points, yet he or she would take no damage. The spell lasts 24 hours or until the protection is used up.</p>\n<p>Once cast, the spell may not be reinforced with further magic points, nor recast until the old spell&rsquo;s protection has been used up.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> Protect Thee from Mighty Blows, Armour of the Will, Blood Shield</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":false},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":900001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/ward.png","effects":[]}
{"name":"Clutch of Nyogtha","permission":{"default":0,"UWCqrgKa2URGCPQQ":3,"rmGdDGeSETHxdMwa":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Keeper Rulebook V7","castingTime":"Instantaneous","cost":{"mp":"1+ magic points equal to twice the damage delivered that round","san":"1D20","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"<p>The caster must spend 1 magic point to begin the spell and the target must be within conversational distance. For the spell to take effect the caster must succeed in an opposed POW roll with the target. If the caster wins the roll, the target feels as though a large hand or tentacle is crushing his or her heart, losing [[/roll 1D3]] hit points for each combat round that the spell is in effect. While under such attack, the target is temporarily paralyzed, as though having a heart attack. In the round that the accumulated damage from this spell reduces hit points to zero, the target&rsquo;s chest ruptures and bursts, and the target&rsquo;s smoking heart appears in the hand of the caster.</p>\n<p>Each round the spell lasts, the caster must spend magic points equal to twice the number of hit points in damage. The caster must concentrate on the spell each round that it is to remain in effect and the caster must defeat the target in an opposed POW roll each round. If the caster is distracted or if the target successfully resists, the spell ends. Any damage already done remains.</p>\n<p><strong>Alternative names:</strong> The Vile Wrench, The Insidious Wrath of the Dark Wizard, Ye Loathsome Tickle.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":true,"gate":false,"combat":true},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"cXrgSU5iPZV9CuHT","sort":200001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-en/pictures/icons/tentacleheart.png","effects":[],"_id":"pS5QsXZaeSRAN9eA"}
